# Code owners. GitHub requests review from the matching owner on PRs that
# touch these paths. This is also the supported replacement for the
# `reviewers:` key that Dependabot removed in Aug 2025 — Dependabot routes
# its bump PRs to the owner of the files they change.
#
# The github-actions Dependabot config bumps `.github/workflows/*` (and the
# trailing version comments there), so owning `.github/` is what puts a
# human in front of every new pinned SHA.
/.github/ @baer
